docs.lead_paragraph: All poultry was banished yesterday from the Thursday menus of public eating places throughout the country and restaurateurs predicted that an egg on the table would be a rarity today.

headline.main: CAFE MENUS TODAY BAN POULTRY, EGGS; Some Places to Offer Game Birds at High Prices -- Tight Observance Is Pledged Today's Restaurant Menus Here Offer Diners No Poultry or Eggs
